                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.48/1571: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Commissioner at Riga</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Young</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-08-23T13:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 23, 1921—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>96. Your 492.</p>
                <p>Amend American Relief Administration party’s passports to include Russia and
                    object of visit to “American Relief Administration”. They are to be permitted to
                    carry passports into Soviet Russia.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
